                    <div class="announcements-list">
                        <div class="announcement-item">
                            <span class="announcement-date">Jun 15</span>
                            <h3 class="text-white-dm">Community Pool Maintenance</h3>
                            <p>The community pool will be closed on June 20th for regular maintenance...</p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">Read More</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="announcement-item">
                            <span class="announcement-date">Jun 10</span>
                            <h3 class="text-white-dm">New Recycling Guidelines</h3>
                            <p>Please review the updated recycling guidelines for our community...</p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">Read More</a>
                        </div>
